# =============================================================================
# .wqmignore — project-scoped index exclusions for workspace-qdrant-mcp
# =============================================================================
# Applied by the daemon ON TOP OF .gitignore and the daemon-wide
# global.wqmignore. Standard gitignore syntax, anchored to this repo root.
# Changes take effect at the next ignore reconciliation (file modified or
# daemon restart).
# =============================================================================

# ─── Semantic-search evaluation artifacts ────────────────────────────────────
# These two files contain the benchmark queries AND their expected file paths
# verbatim. When indexed, they dominate semantic-search results for any query
# about search internals (data leakage) — the eval fixtures outrank the real
# implementation files they point at. The benchmark runner
# (`npm run benchmark:semantic`) reads them straight from disk, so excluding
# them from the INDEX does not affect benchmarking.
src/typescript/mcp-server/reports/
src/typescript/mcp-server/scripts/benchmark-data/
